{"tid":41280,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［Airbnb] 遇到假房主可以點做","createTime":"2016-12-15T18:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T06:44:36.000Z","uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b195b2c918539033add69ed922700581449cb098","tid":41280,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:40:15.000Z","msg":"十一月尾時我上airbnb搵大阪既民宿<br />\n<br />\n搵到一間裝修同設計都唔錯既 之後我聯絡個房主 然後佢用中文同我溝通 最後我好快咁比埋錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為就黎到出發個日 所以我問個房主關於民宿既相關資料<br />\n<br />\n點撚知佢唔撚覆我 跟著我上網搵有關假房主既特徵<br />\n<br />\n又真係中撚曬，包括用中文同我message、覆我覆得好快(訂之前) 、同埋冇住何既評價<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問我係應該直接聯絡airbnb公司講番個情況，睇下有冇得退錢，定係啲錢已經凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6873b7f0c959054bb97b18648c9771c468860d","tid":41280,"uid":11156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:41:13.000Z","msg":"叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caec67839706b811de3de7723354c867bc883e4","tid":41280,"uid":16014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:41:44.000Z","msg":"Call Airbnb，應該可以換房"},{"pid":"3c9a7661b3c6da390183f7f315c2e6f3cb6981c0","tid":41280,"uid":14135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:42:42.000Z","msg":"聯絡airbnb <br />\n冇記錯係住完佢先收到錢"},{"pid":"051115194a873a6a5107505b389f963908d5f934","tid":41280,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你指個房主個名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac7829ab2d0901cc313102cd4c82f5f901ae0fe","tid":41280,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聯絡airbnb <br />\n冇記錯係住完佢先收到錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試下先 係咪email Airbnb?<br />\n同埋有冇話限幾多日前唔可以改架？ <br />\n<br />\n唔該巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa35358bd889f8ee09113a43ab257c2e0e3dc2f","tid":41280,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:28:16.000Z","msg":"住唔到一定有得退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619eb50f284b2c7ac627726757cf752e66ffeb0f","tid":41280,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:43:26.000Z","msg":"你應該即刻book左第二間先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4ecaa7c514e83510a967b619f9ece70f88b4b8","tid":41280,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:21:22.000Z","msg":"Call airbnb 個24hrs hotline"},{"pid":"993eb439d6823addb8e39c70d1c8029449f85e34","tid":41280,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"um....你肯定你係正式官網畀錢就一定冇事<br />\n<br />\n通常呢D唔係要用埋假網先呃到錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5379b58ebb350b886683b7fcafe8d159f4692f2","tid":41280,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:30:39.000Z","msg":"咁撚得人驚"},{"pid":"3462b555d8d0466dab9aeb75aaf55d2af5cbe11a","tid":41280,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:33:43.000Z","msg":"Book Airbnb 一定睇間房既review 先敢book...最少30粒5星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfbc90ba9ce414ec7d7a4151fa204ad7e6741dc","tid":41280,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:49:43.000Z","msg":"點會夠膽租全